io.flutter.embedding.engine.systemchannels

Interface AccessibilityChannel.AccessibilityMessageHandler

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FlutterJNI.AccessibilityDelegate
    Enclosing class:
    AccessibilityChannel

    public static interface AccessibilityChannel.AccessibilityMessageHandler
extends FlutterJNI.AccessibilityDelegate
    Handler that receives accessibility messages sent from Flutter to Android through a given AccessibilityChannel. To register an AccessibilityMessageHandler with a AccessibilityChannel, see AccessibilityChannel.setAccessibilityMessageHandler(AccessibilityMessageHandler).
